---
import { Image } from 'astro:assets';
import codepen from "../assets/brand-codepen.svg"
import linkedin from "../assets/brand-linkedin.svg"
import github from "../assets/brand-github.svg"
---
<section class={"hero"} id="about">
    <h1 class={"hero__title"}>Ramsey <br> Ediku</h1>
    <p>
        I am a developer who loves turning ideas into things people can actually use and enjoy. 
        My interest in coding started back in school and grew into a real passion that led me to study Computer Science and help others learn along the way.
       <br><br>
        I have worked on projects that taught me the value of teamwork, creativity, and constant learning. 
        Right now, I am focused on growing my skills and becoming a well-rounded developer who creates meaningful, user-friendly experiences.
    </p>
    <div class={"hero__links"}>
        <a target="_blank" href="https://linkedin.com/in/ramseyediku"><Image alt="" src={linkedin}></Image></a>
        <a target="_blank" href="http://github.com/ramseyediku"><Image alt="" src={github}></Image></a>
        <a target="_blank" href="mailto:ramseyediku@protonmail.com"><Image alt="" src={github}></Image></a>
        <a target="_blank" href="https://codepen.io/ramseyediku"><Image alt="" src={codepen}></Image></a>
    </div>
</section>

<style>

    .hero {
        .hero__title {
            margin-block: 0 0.45em;
        }
        .hero__links {
            display: flex;
            margin-block: 2.5em 1.5em;
            gap: 2em;

            img {
                --logo-dimension: 1.75em;
                width: var(--logo-dimension);
                height: var(--logo-dimension);
                border-radius: 50%;
                filter: invert(100%) sepia(100%) saturate(0%) hue-rotate(288deg) brightness(102%) contrast(102%);

                &:hover {
                    background-color: black;
                }
            }
        }
    }
   
   
</style>